overview:
Lichi is in charge of leading and driving business development, marketing and monetization for Foound.

He started his professional career at Google in Mountain View, CA. Later on, he relocated to Singapore to join the Google SEA landing team to develop deeper relations with advertisers in the region. His love for digital and mobile advertising eventually led him to AdMob where he was in charge of key accounts, acquiring strategic partners, managing developer communities, hosting developer meet-ups and giving talks at community events. After Google closed the acquisition of AdMob, Lichi left and join Foound in his current position.
